# 2. Component Architecture

## SplashScreen.tsx

Acts as the application's premium loading experience.

### Features

* Animated ambient background
* Logo reveal with glowing effects
* Letter-by-letter title animation
* Simulated loading progress
* Tone.js asset loading indicator
* Developer branding
* Smooth exit transition

---

## Header.tsx

Main navigation bar displayed at the top.

### Features

* Brand logo and application title
* Web MIDI connection status
* Practice statistics access
* Theme switcher
* Fullscreen toggle
* Keyboard mapping help

---

## Piano.tsx & PianoKey.tsx

Core piano interface rendering an interactive 88-key keyboard.

### Features

* Fully playable virtual piano
* Mouse support
* Multi-touch support
* Computer keyboard input
* MIDI controller compatibility
* Falling note visualization
* Active note highlighting
* Scale guide visualization
* Press animations

---

## Controls.tsx

Configuration dashboard for customizing the playing experience.

### Features

* Master volume adjustment
* Instrument selection
* Note label visibility
* Chord detection toggle
* Scale guide selection
* Root note configuration
* Octave shifting for keyboard controls

---

## Metronome.tsx

Timing assistant for practice sessions.

### Features

* Adjustable BPM
* Tap tempo calculation
* Audible click generation
* Visual beat synchronization

---

## Recorder.tsx

Records live piano performances.

### Features

* Real-time note recording
* Timing and velocity capture
* Local storage of recordings
* Playback controls
* Stop functionality
* Recording deletion

---

## PracticeScoreboard.tsx

Displays practice performance after song completion.

### Metrics

* Total notes played
* Accuracy percentage
* Current streak
* Maximum streak
* Overall performance grade (S, A, B, C, F)
* Motivational feedback

---

## SongLibrary.tsx

Interactive collection of practice songs.

### Features

* Built-in song library
* Custom song support
* Sequential note highlighting
* Interactive play-along mode
* Wait Mode requiring correct key presses before continuing

---

## SongCreator.tsx

Allows users to compose and save custom songs.

### Features

* Input validation
* Conversion of note sequences into structured playback data
* Local persistence through Zustand

---

## KeyboardRemapper.tsx

Customizes QWERTY keyboard mappings.

### Features

* User-defined key assignments
* Reset to default layouts
* Persistent configuration storage

---

## StatsModal.tsx

Displays long-term learning analytics.

### Statistics

* Total notes played
* Practice duration
* Number of sessions
* Last practice date
* Key usage heatmap
* Playing activity visualization

