# 4. Global State Management (settings.ts)

The centralized Zustand store manages both persistent and runtime application data.

## Persistent Settings

* Theme preference
* Volume level
* Instrument selection
* Keyboard remapping
* Saved recordings
* Custom songs
* Favorites
* Practice statistics

## Runtime State

* Active song playback
* Loop and shuffle controls
* Metronome configuration
* Active pressed keys
* Note history

## Performance Tracking

* Scores
* Hit and miss counts
* Accuracy calculations
* Combo streaks
* Session statistics

---

# 5. Custom Hooks & Utilities

## useAudio.ts

Responsible for:

* Loading piano samples
* Managing Tone.js playback
* Pitch interpolation
* Audio effects
* Triggering note start/stop events

---

## useKeyboard.ts

Handles:

* Global keyboard listeners
* Key press and release events
* QWERTY-to-note mapping
* Sustain pedal behavior

---

## useMetronome.ts

Provides:

* Scheduled beat generation
* BPM synchronization
* Timing utilities

---

## chordDetector.ts

Analyzes simultaneously played notes to identify common chord structures, including:

* Major
* Minor
* Diminished
* Dominant 7th
* Suspended 4th
* Other interval-based harmonies

